    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246240/extras/452879dc3f09bef1ad02c8a2dd7579cc.poster.avif?t=1738223981\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246240/extras/452879dc3f09bef1ad02c8a2dd7579cc.webm?t=1738223981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246240/extras/452879dc3f09bef1ad02c8a2dd7579cc.mp4?t=1738223981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公在生活中总是莫名其妙地被困在密室中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >简单却有意味深长的谜题层出不穷，解开谜底的瞬间令人倍感畅快。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>■第二章</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逃脱舞台设在位于住宅区和公寓林立的区域里的一栋带有历史气息的“旧学校校区”。主人公原本只是想偷偷进去试试胆量，却不小心被困住了？！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在世界一隅的闹鬼的旧校区中，一场逃脱剧即将拉开帷幕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246240/extras/3d2232202f096f44f330df494554c3d5.poster.avif?t=1738223981\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246240/extras/3d2232202f096f44f330df494554c3d5.webm?t=1738223981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246240/extras/3d2232202f096f44f330df494554c3d5.mp4?t=1738223981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏采用了全3D画面和各种巧妙机关，操作体验顺畅，包括多重结局。配备便条、相机功能等，确保从新手到逃脱专家都能简单地享受“解谜”乐趣的逃脱游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各个故事独立成章，可从随意情境开始体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>■欢迎参与 Let's Plays！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎随时通过我们的官方账号与我们联系！</p>",
